    "comment_regular_data": [
        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Let's do the full revert of cfcdbcf638b5957213b3c1a55d5d1b5659a2fb3e here. It's not clear we need `config.buftypes`. \r\n\r\nI wrote my understanding of the landscape [here](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/36775#issuecomment-4106304954). Please discuss in this PR if necessary.\r\n\r\n",
